Acknowledgment: the audio-derived auto-haptics in this project were inspired by the
earlier auto-haptics work of loteran on the DS5Dongle. While the DSP and related
code here were independently rewritten, loteran's original experiments — in
particular relocating `state_set` to RAM, which enabled haptic actuation at stock
clock speeds — were the foundation that made this feature possible. With thanks.


